node.text: This is Wings of Rescue. Our sponsor, @titosvodka, will match up to $20,000 in donations sent their way through the link in our bio. Wings of Rescue flies dogs like Clyde from overcrowded shelters and disaster areas to shelters with empty kennel space where they’ll be adopted in no time. They’ve saved 8,597 pets this year already and can save way more with your help. Everyone involved gets a 14/10 from us [EDIT: initial goal of $20k hit in 45 minutes, secondary goal of $40k hit in 3 1/2 hours]

node.text: This is Blueberry. He’s learning to be a guard dog. Right now he’s more like the welcome wagon. 12/10 (follow @blueberry_weimaraptor)

An adorable light brown weimaraner with blue eyes is jumping towards the camera
An adorable light brown weimaraner with blue eyes is looking up at the camera with a huge smile.
A puppy golden retriever has some shrubbery in his mouth. He is trotting around the yard with his human close behind. The human is wearing blue jeans and a black tee shirt.

node.text: This is Max. He’s an aspiring landscaper. Believes in doing all the hard work himself. Isn’t afraid to get his paws dirty. 13/10 would hire in a heartbeat (follow @gunnydog_drman_anddafloofs)

node.accessibility_caption: A black, brown and white senior dog is outside on the grass wearing a pink lei around her head.

node.text:
This is Loki. She finally joined the retirement club. Planned an elaborate vacation to Hawaii, but decided to bring Hawaii to her instead. 13/10 #SeniorPupSaturday

Loki has had her consultation with @JustFoodForDogs and has decided on the Turkey & Whole Wheat Macaroni diet. You can learn more about their fresh whole food movement by clicking the link in our bio (4th one down) 🤗 #partner

node.accessibility_caption: A black, brown and white senior dog is outside on the grass wearing a pink lei around her head.
A black, brown and white senior dog is outside on the grass wearing a pink lei around her neck
A black, brown and white senior dog is outside on the grass wearing a pink lei around her neck. She’s looking up at the sky, perhaps wistfully.
A black, brown and white senior dog is outside on the grass wearing a pink lei around her neck
A brown pitbull is looking at the camera.

node.text:
This is Hank. He found a big dog bone during a walk and ate it whole before his human could react. It caused an obstruction and he had to have emergency surgery to remove it. We’ve covered the remaining cost for his care. He’s agreed to try really hard not to do it again. 13/10

This week we were sent 115 GoFundMe’s totaling $819,391.42 in requested funds. We sadly can’t post them all. Please consider getting @Trupanion through the link in our bio (third one down from there) so you never have to send us one. It’s best to be puppared ❤️ #partner

node.accessibility_caption: A brown pitbull is looking at the camera.
A brown pitbull is laying on the couch.

A screenshot showing that WeRateDogs has covered the rest of this dog’s fundraiser need. Please consider getting Trupanion medical insurance for the life of your pet, so that you never have to send us your own fundraiser.
Photo by WeRateDogs® on August 27, 2021. May be an image of dog.

node.text: This is Wiggles. He was recently diagnosed with soft tissue sarcoma and had surgery to remove a cancerous lump from his leg. He’s awaiting electrochemotherapy, which is his best chance at full remission. You can help Wiggles keep wiggling through the link in our bio. 13/10 [EDIT: fully funded in 45 minutes]
